{
  "stem": "27409.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, you see, it was-- you got free, so you went back to Nahariyyah and worked.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked in different jobs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But because the school started to reorganize schools, so I worked as a teacher.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I was not in the army I was a local mobilization officer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Obviously I get-- got the job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, there, it didn't have telephone at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was one telephone and-- or two telephones the whole Nahariyyah, which was a village.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now it's a nice town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But by [INAUDIBLE], they came with the motorbike, a soldier brought me the mobilization order.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I had a few men with soldiers in the reserve, which I announced in front of the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They went out and called the other group.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so it went down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In a certain hour you had to move [INAUDIBLE] [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was our uniform.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was working in Nahariyyah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a home for wounded soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she worked in the hotels there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had majordomos, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till my wife fell ill and I had little scolding incident, you could call it so.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was sent also for the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a reconnaissance officer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was sent over to the territory over Syrian territory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Came back.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My job-- I worked in the bank the time-- was gone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All right, during the day I worked in the bank, in the evening I worked in the school, the grammar school, the evening grammar school.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Teaching children which could not have studied normally in schools and wanted to learn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I taught them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I came back, my job was taken by one-- a religious one who did not go to the army.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
